These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different games are played: whist, scrabble, bridge, snooker, go, billiard, canasta
House: ranch-style, tower, futuristic, palace, craftsman, colonial, cottage
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: climbing, golf, parkour, surfing, tennis, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person playing go is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the tower house and the ranch-style house##2
 4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the tower house is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person playing whist is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the palace house is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person playing go##2
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person playing canasta is the futuristic house##1
11. the colonial house is the person playing snooker##1
12. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
13. the person who's sport is climbing is the craftsman house##1
14. the person playing billiard is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Game   | go | whist     | billiard | scrabble | snooker | canasta  | bridge  |
| House   | ranch-style  | palace        | tower  | cottage     | colonial   | futuristic       | craftsman   |
| Sport         | golf   | water-polo | surfing    | parkour  | tennis | volleyball | climbing |

