.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: purple, light-blue, white, ebony, grey, pink, chestnut
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, baccarat, bluemaster, siglo, bolivar, havana, bongani
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, scooter, ship, train, trike
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is the bolivar-smoker##1
 3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the person who likes purple is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person who likes purple is between the bongani-smoker and the person driving the trike##2
 8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
10. the person who likes white is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
12. the person driving the bus is the person who likes light-blue##1
13. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
14. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person driving the train##1
15. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
16. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Color   | pink | chestnut      | ebony     | purple  | grey | white | light-blue |
| Cigar         | baccarat  | pall-mall | havana | bluemaster | bongani | siglo   | bolivar  |
| Transport     | roller   | train     | trike        | scooter  | ship   | car       | bus      |

