 9. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
10. the person who likes ivory is the person playing canasta##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing backgammon##1
12. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
13. the person playing billiard is the person who likes turquise##1
14. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
15. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
16. the person who likes ivory is between the person playing bridge and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
| Color   | orange | azure      | turquise | yellow     | amber     | ivory   | coral |
| Game       | monopoly    | scrabble | billiard    | chess | backgammon     | canasta | bridge |
| Pet        | snake    | goldfish | goat    | rabbit    | guinea-pig | chinchilla | bird |

